extends layout

block head
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,300')
block content
  main.container.m-t-3.m-x-6
    header.m-b-3
      nav
        ul.nav.nav-pills.pull-xs-right
          li.nav-item.active
            a(href='#').nav-link Home
        ul.nav.nav-pills.pull-xs-right
          li.nav-item
            a(href='#').nav-link Login
        ul.nav.nav-pills.pull-xs-right
          li.nav-item
            a(href='#').nav-link About

      h1.text-muted.m-b-3 #{title}

    a(href='https://github.com/JoeBiellik/dynamicdns')
      img(style='position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; border: 0;', src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/github/ribbons/forkme_right_gray_6d6d6d.png', alt='Fork me on GitHub')

    section.jumbotron.p-y-2
      h2.display-4.p-y-2 Simple Dynamic DNS
      p.lead Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus.
      p
        a(href='#').btn.btn-lg.btn-success.text-center.m-t-1 Sign up today

  script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.2.min.js')
  script(src='/main.js')
